01:06.242 --> 01:19.281
And last year in 2025, we challenged all of our North Star churches to keep the main thing, the main thing, which is bringing people to Jesus Christ and a decision to follow Him.

01:19.642 --> 01:25.671
And that's represented not only by those who come forward, but those who follow Christ in baptism.

01:26.352 --> 01:33.042
So we said, hey, 140 churches, can't we just, could we baptize maybe a thousand this past year?

01:34.018 --> 01:47.574
Well, I don't know if maybe you've heard or maybe Pastor Eric has mentioned to you, but we did baptize in our churches, including South Ron, 1,100 people last year.

01:48.435 --> 01:50.897
We can clap because it wasn't us.

01:51.718 --> 01:53.781
It was God working through us.

01:55.162 --> 01:56.904
And it's not just a number.

01:56.944 --> 02:01.970
This represents individuals because we believe that God

02:02.082 --> 02:03.985
is in the details.

02:05.948 --> 02:06.970
God is in the details.

02:08.012 --> 02:12.659
God didn't just so love the world that He sent His only Son.

02:13.641 --> 02:15.003
God so loved you.

02:16.906 --> 02:17.988
There is a difference, right?

02:18.048 --> 02:26.322
I mean, I know you're part of the world, but when we personalize it and we realize that God is interested in each one of us.

02:27.682 --> 02:42.878
And I've shared with you many times in the times that I've had the privilege of being here and sharing the gospel and sharing from God's word here from this pulpit that God is not just the God of eternity, but He's the God of every moment.

02:44.139 --> 02:48.003
